{
  "stem": "14429.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was reading.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I hear the boots coming up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I am petrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know what is happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I am immobilized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can hardly breathe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I haven't slept yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Nazis came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was a man that was looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he gets paid per head for the Jews that he finds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he found us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was looking whether we were home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And they come in, three of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I'm in my room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I hear my father talking outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I go out-- get out of bed, and I stand in the middle of my room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The door is closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My father comes in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the German comes in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I'm standing in the middle, and I'm paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I cannot move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my father begs him, please, go out, let my daughter get dressed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You seen what condition she's in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He decided to walk out of my room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My father had to help me dress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't even dress myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I remember the remark that, that one German said-- made.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had a map on the wall, and with little flags, we were following the front line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I remember him saying, I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The Jews are not allowed to have radios, he said in German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they all know where the front line is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anyway, the three of us were taken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Our apartment was sealed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were put into prison, into a prison, common prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Where I was, was like a holding cell, holding pen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And there I met other Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
